00:17:16.660 --> 00:17:18.660
What are you thinking?

00:17:21.420 --> 00:17:23.420
Nothing...

00:17:23.420 --> 00:17:28.700
You seem so quiet.

00:17:30.700 --> 00:17:31.380
I don't know what to say.

00:17:31.380 --> 00:17:33.800
Whom are you thinking of?

00:17:35.800 --> 00:17:37.800
Nope!

00:17:47.800 --> 00:17:51.360
It's really tasty!

00:18:09.080 --> 00:18:11.080
Your mouth is dirty.

00:18:11.080 --> 00:18:13.080
Really?

00:18:13.080 --> 00:18:14.880
Right here.

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:15.480
Here?

00:18:15.480 --> 00:18:17.480
Right here... here....

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:18.940
Here?

