Right here

00:18:21.860 --> 00:18:23.120
Here?

00:18:23.120 --> 00:18:25.120
Right here...

00:18:26.700 --> 00:18:28.420
Here?

00:18:30.420 --> 00:18:32.420
Here...

00:18:38.340 --> 00:18:40.340
Don't be slick!

00:18:41.440 --> 00:18:43.440
Seduce me, don't you?

00:18:43.440 --> 00:18:45.440
